# DSC291 Final Project: KV Cache Compression Analysis

## Overview
A systematic analysis of KV cache compression policies (Streaming, H2O, SnapKV) for long-context inference.

## Environment
- Google Colab, A100 40GB GPU
- LLaMA-2-7B-Chat (FP16)
- Transformers 4.44.2

## Files
- `DSC291ai__20__fixed.ipynb` - Main experiment notebook
- `report.pdf` - Final report

